      <title>World markets respond to Trump's new tariffs. And, TikTok nears its sell-by date</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/04/03/g-s1-57936/up-first-newsletter-trump-tariffs-tiktok-leasing-algorithm</link>
